---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Approach — Arcbrim Exotics"
  description="How Arcbrim Exotics approaches every acquisition and placement engagement."
  current="approach"
>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label">Approach</p>
      <h1>We do not operate like a dealership.<br />We operate like a trusted advisor.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container"><div class="rule"></div></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="col-label"><p class="label">Philosophy</p></div>
        <div class="col-content">
          <h2>Authority-led. Relationship-first.</h2>
          <p>Arcbrim does not sell. Every conversation is diagnostic — designed to confirm alignment rather than persuade. If your objectives, timeline, and standards align with how we work, we proceed. If they do not, we say so plainly.</p>
          <p>This selectivity is not exclusivity for its own sake. It is how we protect the quality of every engagement we take on.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container"><div class="rule"></div></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="col-label"><p class="label">Discretion</p></div>
        <div class="col-content">
          <h2>Your position is never exposed prematurely.</h2>
          <p>Whether you are acquiring or placing a vehicle, your identity and intent are protected throughout the engagement. We introduce you only when the time is right and the alignment is confirmed.</p>
          <p>Discretion is not a feature we offer. It is the foundation of how we operate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container"><div class="rule"></div></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="col-label"><p class="label">Standards</p></div>
        <div class="col-content">
          <h2>Every engagement meets the same standard.</h2>
          <p>We coordinate inspection, transport, title, and all necessary parties so the transaction proceeds with certainty. Our role is to reduce friction and eliminate surprises — not to simply connect parties and step aside.</p>
          <p>The outcome is a transaction that reflects the seriousness of the vehicles and the clients involved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container"><div class="rule"></div></div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="cta-headline">If this approach resonates, an introduction is the appropriate next step.</h2>
      <a href="/inquiry" class="cta">Request an Introduction</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0 clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.2;
    max-width: 26ch;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .rule {
    height: 1px;
    background-color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .section {
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
  }

  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .col-label { padding-top: 0.5rem; }

  .col-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .col-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .col-content p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .cta-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.2;
    max-width: 30ch;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    border: 1px solid rgba(184, 154, 90, 0.4);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    transition: background-color 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
  }

  .cta:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-gold-muted);
    border-color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .two-col {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
